overview: Bodies blend in with geological processes enduring millennia, characters anchored in between fashion and local mythology defy the harsh nature of the high Alps, humans and archaic lichens are hybridized.
tagline: The Grossglockner massif in the Austrian Alps, vernacular motifs, local costumes as well as customs and the structural defiance of the Grossglockner High Alpine Road against the natural force of the mountain into one symbolic amalgam
title: Lichthöhe
